StockVolitility_ROTC_Data <- ROTCDailyTrading_Data %>% 
  left_join(., ListFirm %>% 
              .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "TSE", "",  "IPOFail")], 
            by = "") %>% 
  select("", "TSE", "IPOFail", "", everything()) %>% 
  setDT() %>% 
  .[order(``, ``)] %>% 
  .[!(which( == "8454 " & abs(``) > 90))] %>% 
  # 2014/9/9
  .[, tail(.SD, 90), by = ""]

# data

# Market Model 
MarketReturn_Data_ToJoin <- MarketReturn_Data %>% 
  setnames(., c("", "(%)"), c("Market", "MarketReturn(%)")) %>% 
  .[, Market := case_when(
    Market == "OTC99 OTC " ~ "OTC", 
    Market == "Y9999 " ~ "TSE"
  )] %>% 
  .[, -c(3)]

IdiosyncraticVolatilityData_ToJoin <- ROTCDailyTrading_Data %>% 
  left_join(., ListFirm %>% 
              .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "TSE", "Market", "",  "IPOFail")], 
            by = "") %>% 
  select("", "TSE", "IPOFail", "", everything()) %>% 
  setDT() %>% 
  .[order(``, ``)] %>% 
  .[!(which( == "8454 " & abs(``) > 90))] %>% 
  # 2014/9/9
  .[, tail(.SD, 90), by = ""] %>% 
  .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "Market", "TSE", "", "IPOFail", "", "")]

# data
IdiosyncraticVolatilityData <- IdiosyncraticVolatilityData_ToJoin %>% 
  left_join(., MarketReturn_Data_ToJoin, by = c("", "Market")) %>% 
  setDT() %>% 
  .[, `:=` (AbnormalFirmReturn = `` - , 
            AbnormalMarketReturn = `MarketReturn(%)` - )]

GetMarketModelResiduals <- function(Data, Firm){
  
  CompanyData <- Data %>% 
    .[`` == Firm]
  
  MarketModel <- lm(`AbnormalFirmReturn` ~ `AbnormalMarketReturn`, data = CompanyData)
  
  SDResidual <- sd(MarketModel$residuals)
    
  return(SDResidual)
}

IdiosyncraticVolatility_AfterIPO_Data <- AllFirm_Trading02_16 %>% 
  left_join(., ListFirm %>% 
              .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "TSE", "",  "IPOFail")], 
            by = "") %>% 
  setDT() %>% 
  .[`` >= ``] %>% 
  .[, head(.SD, 250), by = ""] %>% 
  left_join(., FourFactorsVariables_Data, by = "") %>% 
  setDT() %>% 
  .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "TSE", "", "IPOFail", 
                       "", "", "", "(3)",
                       "", "")]

GetMarketModelResiduals <- function(Data, Firm){
  
  CompanyData <- Data %>% 
    .[`` == Firm]
  
  MarketModel <- lm(`` ~ 
                      ``+ `(3)`+ ``+ ``, 
                    data = CompanyData)
  
  SDResidual <- sd(MarketModel$residuals)
    
  return(SDResidual)
  
}

3. Zero Trading Days

  • The percentage of zero trading days in ROTC (Three months prior IPO)

  • ZeroTradingDays_ToJoin data

  • Summary IPOFailZero Trading Ratio (28.46% v.s. 23.39%)

ZeroTradingDays_Data <- ROTCDailyTrading_Data %>% 
  left_join(., ListFirm %>% 
              .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "TSE", "",  "IPOFail")], 
            by = "") %>% 
  select("", "TSE", "IPOFail", "", everything()) %>% 
  setDT() %>% 
  .[order(``, ``)] %>% 
  .[!(which( == "8454 " & abs(``) > 90))] %>% 
  # 2014/9/9
  .[, tail(.SD, 90), by = ""]

ZeroTradingDays <- ZeroTradingDays_Data %>% 
  .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "TSE", 
                       "IPOFail", "", "", "()")] %>% 
  .[, TradingDays := .N, by = ""] %>% 
  .[, ZeroTradingDays := ifelse(`()` ==0, 1, 0) %>% sum, , by = ""] %>%
  .[, ZeroTradingDaysRatio := (ZeroTradingDays / TradingDays)*100] %>% 
  .[, tail(.SD, 1), by = ""]

#  ZeroTradingDays 
ZeroTradingDays %>%
  select(everything()) %>%
  kable("html", escape = F, align = "l") %>%
  kable_styling("hover", full_width = T) %>% 
  scroll_box(width = "800px", height = "500px")

4. Zero Return Days

  • The percentage of zero return days in ROTC (Three months prior IPO)

  • ZeroReturnDays_ToJoin data

  • Summary IPOFailZero Return Ratio (35.87% v.s. 32.71%) (32.22 v.s. 24.44)

ZeroReturnDays_Data <- ROTCDailyTrading_Data %>% 
  left_join(., ListFirm %>% 
              .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "TSE", "",  "IPOFail")], 
            by = "") %>% 
  select("", "TSE", "IPOFail", "", everything()) %>% 
  setDT() %>% 
  .[order(``, ``)] %>% 
  .[!(which( == "8454 " & abs(``) > 90))] %>% 
  # 2014/9/9
  .[, tail(.SD, 90), by = ""]

ZeroReturnDays <- ZeroReturnDays_Data %>% 
  .[, .SD, .SDcols = c("", "TSE", 
                       "IPOFail", "", "", "")] %>% 
  .[, TradingDays := .N, by = ""] %>% 
  .[, ZeroReturnDays := ifelse(`` ==0, 1, 0) %>% sum, , by = ""] %>%
  .[, ZeroReturnDaysRatio := (ZeroReturnDays / TradingDays)*100] %>% 
  .[, tail(.SD, 1), by = ""]
